{"data":[{"id":564169150,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1877b31c64c587bd968ffd1d9de5167e","url_token":"gao-lin-si-man-15","name":"克里斯蒂亚诺梅东","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-80b5baea29466ae5eb7786ab29ad4022_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-80b5baea29466ae5eb7786ab29ad4022_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1877b31c64c587bd968ffd1d9de5167e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564169150","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546337711,"updated_time":1546338596,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e这让我想到了另一个证明事件。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e费马大定律都证了多少年几代数学家的验证和新猜想才能越来越接近证明。直到93年才被安德鲁怀尔斯证明，而且当时他的那一大片证明还有错误，再时隔两年和很多当时数学家合作，95年才修改好，完整的贴出费马大定律的证明公式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1637年，费马在书本空白处提出费马猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1770年，欧拉证明n=3时定理成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1823年，勒让德证明n=5时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1832年，狄利克雷试图证明n=7失败，但证明 n=14时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1839年，拉梅证明n=7时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1850年，库默尔证明2\u0026lt;n\u0026lt;100时除37、59、67三数外定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1955年，范迪维尔以电脑计算证明了 2\u0026lt;n\u0026lt;4002时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1976年，瓦格斯塔夫以电脑计算证明 2\u0026lt;n\u0026lt;125000时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1985年，罗瑟以电脑计算证明2\u0026lt;n\u0026lt;41000000时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1987年，格朗维尔以电脑计算证明了 2\u0026lt;n\u0026lt;101800000时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1995年，怀尔斯证明 n\u0026gt;2时定理成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一位高中生4版纸要证明哥德巴赫猜想，是不是太不自量力了。而且安德鲁怀尔斯可是辞职专门闭关来证明这一他的梦想，而高中生是功利的要保送清北，很让人哭笑不得，让人不知从何说起。不能单说是这个高中生的问题，也有别的方面的问题。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"这让我想到了另一个证明事件。费马大定律都证了多少年几代数学家的验证和新猜想才能越来越接近证明。直到93年才被安德鲁怀尔斯证明，而且当时他的那一大片证明还有错误，再时隔两年和很多当时数学家合作，95年才修改好，完整的贴出费马大定律的证明公式。16…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=333\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccom